title: Minecraft has cascades now?
author: doctor4t
description:
Minecraft has cascades now? Since my Minecraft splash mod basing itself on the Minecraft Caves & Cliffs Part II trailer effects has made quite a splash, I received requests to also add the cascade / waterfall mist effect also seen in the trailer, so I did! Enjoy this Minecraft mod for 1.18 while we patiently wait for the Wild Update.

Download Effective!
